Love is in the air and Bartleby has a business meeting in the country of japan. What better way to show his appreciation to his sugar baby than to take him bitch to the country of Japan for a lovely Onsen Adventure~?
Like what I do? Then why not join my patron for some extra good shit: https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
